                  <!--  *************************************  <decoDesc>  *********************************     -->
                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote>
                        <p>bust of a woman, her head turned slightly to the left, her left hand
                           holding a spindle and a distaff, her right hand touching her cheek and
                           chin; she wears a tunic and a cloak draped over her head and arranged
                           symmetrically on both shoulders and over her arms; a turban and a
                           headband conceal the hair on her forehead, but two locks of hair are
                           visible above each ear, and long locks fall down to her shoulders below;
                           her jewelry consists of a bracelet on each wrist, a necklace of beads,
                           pendant earrings, and a ring on the third finger of her right hand; for
                           her facial features, she has large eyes, with the pupils not indicated,
                           and with a ridge for the upper eyelid; her mouth is a straight line, with
                           a triangular indentation at the corners, and with thin lips</p>
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
